## üé® Customization Guide

### Easy Customization Points
1. **Colors**: Update CSS custom properties in `:root`
2. **Content**: Modify text content in HTML
3. **Features**: Add/remove feature cards
4. **Testimonials**: Update user feedback sections
5. **CTAs**: Customize button text and actions

### Color Scheme Variables
```css
:root {
    --primary-cyan: #00E5FF;
    --accent-purple: #8B5CF6;
    --accent-pink: #EC4899;
    --bg-primary: #000000;
    --text-primary: #ffffff;
}
```

